#E Commerce App using HTML,CSS,JS

A brief description of what this project does and who it's for


## Features

- Light/dark mode toggle
- Fullscreen mode
- Cross platform
- This site got 4 webpages.i.e Home,Contact us,product,Account page.
- Account page got Login and Registeration pages.


## Tech Used

For Backend : JavaScript

For FrontEnd : HTML 5.0,CSS

For Styling Purposes: Google fonts


